<TITLE> Girl, 13, kills boy, 10 </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, June 8 (bdnews24.com)-- A 13-year old has killed a 10-year old by dunking him into a water tank. The incident occurred in Rasulpur village of Dhaka's Keraniganj. The victim 'Hridoy' used to stay with his parents at a rented house. His mother, 'Rubina' said Hridoy was playing with his two younger brothers, 'Arif', 5, and 'Alam', 3, in their yard. She began to look for him once she noticed that Hridoy was not around. After sometime, 'Saima', who lived in the neighbouring house, told her to look in the water tank. She found him there, dead. Police reached the spot and recovered the body after receiving information of the boy's death. Keraniganj police chief Asaduzzaman told bdnews24.com, "Saima admitted that she had pushed Hridoy into the tank and closed its lid." However, the reason behind the murder could not be ascertained. The police have taken Saima into custody. The body has been sent for autopsy and a case was under way. bdn
